COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 18px; padding-bottom: 48px;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n  Er is op <b>zondag, 15 februari 16:17</b> met <b>Google Chromebook</b> ingelogd op je 2dehands-account (<b>denisvalerievichmayorov1@gmail.com</b>). Je hebt nog niet eerder vanaf dit toestel ingelogd op je 2dehands-account. We sturen je deze mail om er zeker van te zijn dat jij het was.<br/><br/>\r\nAls je net hebt ingelogd, hoef je verder niks te doen.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\n<b>Ik was het niet</b>\r\n<br/>\r\nAls je niet hebt ingelogd, stel dan een nieuw wachtwoord in via onderstaande link.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td><table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n            <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td style=\"-webkit-border-radius: 3px; -moz-border-radius: 3px; border-radius: 3px;\" bgcolor=\"#116DB4\">\r\n                    <a href=\"https://www.2dehands.be/identity/v2/reset-password?utm_source=systemmail&utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; text-decoration: none; -webkit-border-radius: 3px; -moz-border-radius: 3px; border-radius: 3px; padding: 8px 18px; border: 1px solid #116DB4; display: inline-block; background-color: #116DB4;\">\r\n                        <strong>Nieuw wachtwoord instellen</strong>\r\n                    </a>\r\n                </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n        </table></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br/>\r\n<b>Je account beter beschermen?</b>\r\n<br/>\r\nMet de sms-beveiligingscontrole is jouw 2dehands-account voortaan nog beter beschermd. Meer weten? <a style=\"color:#21479c; text-decoration:none\" href=\"https://help.2dehands.be/s/article/bescherm-je-account-met-de-sms-beveiligingscontrole-2dehands?utm_source=systemmail&utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\">Hier</a> leggen we het uitgebreid uit.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n                                <br>\r\n                                    <div>Met vriendelijke groeten,</div>\r\n                                    <div>Het 2dehands-team</div>\r\n                                </td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                            </tbody>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"full-width\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-top: 1px #f0efed solid; max-width: 600px\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td style=\"MAX-WIDTH: 600px;WIDTH: 600px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top; PADDING-BOTTOM: 32px; PADDING-TOP: 24px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #fff; text-align: center;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"display: inline-block\">\r\n            <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=be.tweedehands.m&hl=nl\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"DISPLAY: block\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://s.2dehands.be/email/res/images/playstore@2x.png\" width=\"135\" height=\"40\"></a></td>\r\n                <td width=\"10\" style=\"font-size:1px; line-height:1px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n                <td><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id567722021?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"DISPLAY: block\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://s.2dehands.be/email/res/images/appstore@2x.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\"></a></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n        </table></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class=\"full-width\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 600px\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td style=\"MAX-WIDTH: 600px; WI